<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="165" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="165">Diagnosis.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="165">Slender and either opaque or translucent body. Collarette absent or small (almost absent). Intestinal diverticula present or absent. Grasping spines not serrated. Two rows of teeth. Two pairs of lateral fins completely rayed.</paragraph>
